00039 MTKt_status MtkFileCoreMetaDataQuery(
00040   const char *filename, 
00041   int *nparam, 
00042   char ***paramlist  )
00043 {
00044   MTKt_status status_code; /* Return status of this function */
00045   MTKt_status status;
00046   int32 hdf_status;        /* HDF-EOS return status */
00047   int32 sd_id = FAIL;      /* HDF SD file identifier. */
00048 
00049   if (filename == NULL)
00050     MTK_ERR_CODE_JUMP(MTK_NULLPTR);
00051 
00052   /* Open HDF File */
00053   hdf_status = sd_id = SDstart(filename, DFACC_READ);
00054   if (hdf_status == FAIL)
00055     MTK_ERR_CODE_JUMP(MTK_HDF_SDSTART_FAILED);
00056 
00057   /* Read coremetadata. */
00058   status = MtkFileCoreMetaDataQueryFid(sd_id, nparam, paramlist);
00059   MTK_ERR_COND_JUMP(status);
00060 
00061   /* Close HDF File */
00062   hdf_status = SDend(sd_id);
00063   if (hdf_status == FAIL)
00064     MTK_ERR_CODE_JUMP(MTK_HDF_SDEND_FAILED);
00065   sd_id = FAIL;
00066 
00067   return MTK_SUCCESS;
00068 
00069 ERROR_HANDLE:
00070   if (sd_id != FAIL)
00071     SDend(sd_id);
00072 
00073   return status_code;
00074 }
